{"tid":1145928,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「股神」巴菲特旗艦 巴群墮龐氏騙局 損失逾3.97億美元","createTime":"2019-05-09T02:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T02:41:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"82db6d5c96fd10d2c01132cf298c6a513e11debe","tid":1145928,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"「股神」畢非德(Warren Buffett)投資旗艦巴郡(Berkshire Hathaway)公布，因為投資了一個懷疑欺騙的太陽能發電項目，須撥備3.77億美元(22.93億港元)。<br />\n<br />\n巴郡上周六公布首季財務報告，指出在2015至2018年期間曾投資3.4億美元在多個稅務股本投資基金，直至該公司獲悉聯邦執法人員指控該等基金的贊助人涉及欺詐行為。<br />\n<br />\n巴郡周三進一步表示，有理由相信投資者預期的利得稅得益將不會出現。畢非德助理Debbie Bosanek證實，有關投資涉及DC Solar。<br />\n<br />\nDC Solar未有回應傳媒相關查詢。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月，DC Solar申請破產保護。聯邦調查局探員其後表示，該公司經營模式很可能是一個龐氏騙局。美國證券交易委員會也提控DC Solar涉嫌龐氏騙局。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2132876/畢非德旗艦墮龐氏騙局+損失逾22億\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2132876%2F%E7%95%A2%E9%9D%9E%E5%BE%B7%E6%97%97%E8%89%A6%E5%A2%AE%E9%BE%90%E6%B0%8F%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80%2B%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%E9%80%BE22%E5%84%84&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyftArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=edbb6cf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2132876/畢非德旗艦墮龐氏騙局+損失逾22億</a>"},{"pid":"f8e1ca426933a91dbd92c87c388193f8d7a8b57c","tid":1145928,"uid":175112,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"巴菲特：跌左啲散紙添。。"},{"pid":"aba31033fdf2d6d6c29b78c10ebf12d4373a40c2","tid":1145928,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"巴群"},{"pid":"2a48acd49f4a6a8cef96d5d88920316785ed8a11","tid":1145928,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aba31033fdf2d6d6c29b78c10ebf12d4373a40c2","tid":1145928,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"巴群"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T02:36:17.000Z","msg":"我加落去打錯3.77億美元都係<img src